data.description: Cute cottage-like home. 3 bedrooms & 2 baths sits on a corner lot waiting. Updated cabinets, kitchen counter tops, bathrooms, roof, electrical & fixtures.  Have a gathering on your deck & nice sized backyard that is privately fenced with a metal fence.   The large backyard also offers a storage building & a dog run for your furbabies! Yes!  It's all here! Welcome home! * SELLER GIVING $3,000 IN CLOSING COSTS WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER *Fridge, microwave, oven/range, washer and dryer convey.
